{"tid":1746844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈，聽日邊個唔投票就係支持警暴 一國一制","createTime":"2019-11-23T02:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:58:50.000Z","uid":52658,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6b4923be73ac917ff8ad2d561831f008de4e58","tid":1746844,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"投唔一定贏 但唔投就輸撚硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地搞左咁耐 半年 而家比票你唔投？<br />\n學咩撚野人講光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手係連儂牆同人講<br />\n唔投即係支持政府<br />\n你點對得住無數個被捕 甚至被殺既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n區議會好多時都係數十票之微<br />\n所以唔好覺得自己既票無用<br />\n點用柯文哲會贏到丁守中？<br />\n因為係後生仔同學生係當日 全部拉大隊投佢<br />\n<br />\n唔洗驚有人搞事<br />\n要話比人聽 聽日全日支持警察嚴正執法<br />\n見到黑衣人搞事 燒票站 要即時報警<br />\n15分鐘內警察唔到 就知邊個係度搞事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcac4b7af304a4305cccac38410f1a47578b0a8f","tid":1746844,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:56:23.000Z","msg":"終極焦土派：就係要一國一制攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d976946593ac5d863bfebd77b75d5fc1b17ce3d7","tid":1746844,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T02:56:24.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"90e1ebcd3cf2b620ebe9e418836b7cfdead6008f","tid":1746844,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a6c4cb01dded7afba9ab54762b114ff0e00e8b","tid":1746844,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T03:08:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ec5e51cf757656ebc94a2d219e2c2eeb4